title: Hawaii - Volume 1
description: 10 Hawaiian island style acoustic tracks for your happy moments with multiple loops and shorter edits
longDescription:
Preview the collection:

  • YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j1p_H2cA1gU


"Hawaii - Volume 1" features 10 Hawaiian island style themes suitable for your tropical worlds.

The arrangements include premium tenor ukulele, steel guitar, marimba, guitars and many types of percussions.

Every music theme comes with multiple loops and shorter edits for further usage.


  • Turtles: Full length (01:34), 2 Short edits, 5 Loops
  • Hawaiian Jam: Full length (01:36), 2 Short edits, 7 Loops
  • Kaneohe Moon: Full length (02:51), 2 Short edits, 7 Loops
  • White Sand: Full length (01:24), 2 Short edits, 8 Loops
  • Suppa Flash Ukulele: Full length (01:37), 2 Short edits, 7 Loops
  • Hawaiian Luau: Full length (01:31), 2 Short edits, 8 Loops
  • Kalakaua Avenue: Full length (00:35), 1 Short edit, 3 Loops
  • Strumming My Ukulele In Waikiki: Full length (02:49), Solo, 4 Short edits, 11 Loops
  • Bubbles: Full length (01:41), 2 Short edits, 5 Loops
  • Hawaiian Lava: Full length (02:05), 3 Short edit, 6 Loops
